Sentencas: Additive manufacturing represents a revolution due to its unique capabilities for freeform fabrication of near net shapes with strong reduction of waste material and capital cost.
Titulo: Three-dimensional printed yttria-stabilized zirconia self-supported electrolytes for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: These unfair advantages are especially relevant for expensive and energy-demanding manufacturing processes of advanced ceramics such as Yttria-stabilized Zirconia, the state-of-the-art electrolyte in Solid Oxide Fuel Cell applications.
Titulo: Three-dimensional printed yttria-stabilized zirconia self-supported electrolytes for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: In this study, self-supported electrolytes of yttria-stabilized zirconia have been printed by using a stereolithography three-dimensional printer.
Titulo: Three-dimensional printed yttria-stabilized zirconia self-supported electrolytes for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: Printed electrolytes and complete cells fabricated with cathode and anode layers of lanthanum strontium manganite- and nickel oxide-yttria-stabilized zirconia composites, respectively, were electrochemical characterized showing full functionality.
Titulo: Three-dimensional printed yttria-stabilized zirconia self-supported electrolytes for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: In addition, more complex configurations of the electrolyte have been printed yielding an increase of the performance entirely based on geometrical aspects.
Titulo: Three-dimensional printed yttria-stabilized zirconia self-supported electrolytes for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: Complementary, a numerical model has been developed and validated as predictive tool for designing more advanced configurations that will enable highly performing and fully customized devices in the next future.
Titulo: Three-dimensional printed yttria-stabilized zirconia self-supported electrolytes for solid oxide fuel cell applications
